New Records: Antetokounmpo's 432nd double-double in his career passes Kareem Abdul-Jabbar for the most such games in Bucks history

Post-Match Reflections: The Bucks are above the play-in threshold and should be able to hold on for a move up from that spot if they continue playing their best basketball
